snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | Season 7: Rise of Darkness | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Overwatch 2 Season 7: Rise of Darkness launches October 10!

Return to Halloween Terror in the new Trials of Sanctuary Game Mode and defeat a darkness that threatens everything in its grasp.

Unlock the newest Mythic Skin, Onryō Hanzo

Feel the breeze in the tropical new Control map, Samoa.

Take Sombra and Roadhog for a spin with their new reworks.

Enjoy an all-new Battle Pass, spooky new rewards, and SO much more.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_
